      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I just re-read the logs. The Deep Sleep command is flagged as a 'permanent' state. If we execute this, the probability of the rover successfully completing the primary geological survey mission drops to near 0%. \n\nCan you run a quick simulation of the power levels if we just cut the non-essential science instruments instead of the full system shutdown?",
